  "description_html": "<p><strong style=\"color: #000000;\">Description: Physical bot required</strong></p>\n<div class=\"position-relative\">\n<ul>\n<li>Teams are expected to reach the mentioned goal in a maze with an automatic rover or by teleoperation using the given clues.</li>\n<li>The team with the highest points will be the winner of the challenge!</li>\n<li>Teams will have the option to navigate their rover through the maze in either teleoperation mode or autonomous mode.</li>\n<li>Points will be awarded for successfully escaping the maze, finding hidden objects, time efficiency, and more.</li>\n<li>Don't miss this exciting opportunity to showcase your skills and creativity!</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Team &amp; Registration Rules</strong>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Team size: </span><strong>1 to 4 members</strong></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Multiple teams per institution are allowed</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Registration must be completed </span><strong>at least 2 days prior</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to the event</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Each team must nominate </span><strong>one team leader</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for communication</span></li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Robot Specifications</strong>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The robot must be </span><strong>fully autonomous</strong></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Teleoperation or remote control</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is allowed during the run(Partial score will be awarded)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maximum robot weight: </span><strong>5 kg</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (including battery and all attachments)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Robot dimensions: Refer rule book</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The robot must be </span><strong>self-powered</strong></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Robots must not damage the arena or maze structure</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
